发信人: binfan (扬帆), 信区: WoW<br />标  题: 种族技能都改了，牛兽亡nerf了<br />发信站: 水木社区 (Sun Sep  7 11:12:15 2008), 站内<br /><br />蓝帖翻译,新改的种族天赋<br /><br />这里没有被提到种族天赋没有任何改变,不是被取消了<br /><br />[::艾泽拉斯国家地理 BBS.NGACN.CC::]<br /><br />Orc<br />- Hardiness now reduces the duration of stun effects by 15%<br /><br />兽人<br />减少15%晕的时间<br /><br />Troll<br />- Racial Passive "The Voodoo Shuffle": Reduces the duration of all movement impairing effects by 15%. Trolls be flippin' out mon!<br /><br />- Berserking: no longer has an activation cost of energy/rage/etc<br /><br />巨魔<br />The Voodoo Shuffle, (巫毒滑步) 减少15%移动限制技能的时间,巨魔可以空翻出去.<br />狂暴 无消耗.(不会再消耗能量什么的)<br /><br />Draenei<br />- Gift of the Naaru: now scales based on the higher of either the caster's Attack Power or Spell Power<br /><br />- Shadow Resistance: reduces the chance to be hit by Shadow spells by 2%<br /><br />德莱尼<br />纳鲁祝福 和施法者的AP或者spell power挂钩(选高的那个)<br />减少被暗系法术击中的机会 2%.<br /><br /><br />Dwarf<br />- Frost Resistance: reduces the chance to be hit by Frost spells by 2%<br /><br />- Racial Passive "Mace Specialization": Expertise with Maces and Two-Handed Maces increased by 5.<br /><br />矮人<br />减少被冰系法术击中的机会 2%.<br />锤系专精 锤和双手锤增加5点专精.<br /><br /><br />Undead<br />- Shadow Resistance: reduces the chance to be hit by Shadow spells by 1% (yes, this is lower than the other resistance racials)<br /><br />- Will of the Forsaken: removes any fear, sleep, or charm effect (no longer has a lasting immunity).<br /><br />不死<br />减少被暗系法术击中的机会 1%.比别的种族低.<br />亡灵意志, 移除恐惧,睡眠,诱惑效果.(不再有短时间的免疫效果)<br /><br /><br />Night Elf<br />- Quickness: reduces the chance to be hit by melee or ranged attacks by 2%<br /><br />- Nature Resistance: reduces the chance to be hit by Nature spells by 3%<br /><br />暗夜<br />减少被近程,远程攻击击中的机会 2%.<br />减少被自然系法术击中的机会 3%.<br /><br /><br />Tauren<br />- Endurance: now scales based on base health, to be tuned to approximately a 5% heath increase if the player were wearing green quality gear<br /><br />- Nature Resistance: reduces the chance to be hit by Nature spells by 2%<br /><br />牛头<br />那个增加血量会和基础血量挂钩.绿装玩家会看到大概5%的血量增加.<br />减少被自然系法术击中的机会 2%.<br /><br /><br /><br />Gnome<br />- Escape Artist: the freeing effect can no longer be resisted<br /><br />- Arcane Resistance: reduces the chance to be hit by Arcane spells by 2%<br /><br />侏儒<br />逃脱大师 不可能被抵抗<br />减少被奥然系法术击中的机会 2%.<br /><br /><br /><br />Blood Elf<br />- Mana Tap: ability removed (partially integrated into Arcane Torrent)<br /><br />- Arcane Torrent: restores 15 energy, 15 runic power, or 6% of mana to the Blood Elf (along with the current 2s silence effect)<br /><br />- Magic Resistance: reduces the chance to be hit by spells by 2%<br /><br />血精灵<br />法力分流被移除<br />Arcane Torrent: 回复15能量/符文力/6%的魔法, 同时对周围2秒沉默效果.<br />减少被法术击中的机会 2%.<br /><br />Human   <br />- Perception: changed to a passive, now grants one character level of passive stealth detection<br /><br />- Racial "The Fall of Humanity": Feign death which may trick enemies into ignoring you. Any threat is restored versus enemies still in combat upon cancellation of this effect. 5min cooldown<br /><br />- Racial Passive "Human Supremacy": The dominance of Humanity is evidenced by having one more racial bonus than normal. Actually, make that two counting this one. (just a tooltip, no actual functionality)<br /><br />- The Human Spirit: spirit bonus lowered to 5%<br /><br />人类<br />感知 成为被动,增加一个人物等级的探隐效果<br />The Fall of Humanity,(人性堕落) 假死,让敌人不再攻击你,战斗中起来后仇恨会恢复到假死前的等级. 5分钟CD<br />Human Supremacy,(人类强势) 被动, 没有实际效果. 人类占有绝对优势的证据就是人类比别的种族多一个种族天赋,实际上算上这个的话人类比别的种族多出两个种族天赋.<br />只增加5%的精神<br /><br />--<br /><br />※ 来源:·水木社区 newsmth.net·[FROM: 125.96.110.*]